    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/a8b1678bf5fe9baeb99dd65cfb7edd3f.avif?t=1770945548\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>如果你想了解关于《虚妄之盒》的第一手资讯或福利，欢迎加入QQ群：1015871736 或关注bilibili官方账号@虚妄之盒-制作组。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《虚妄之盒》是一款融合Rougelike卡牌构筑与下落式塔防玩法的快节奏卡牌战斗游戏。养成无敌大哥，打出超燃连击，爽到停不下来！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>爽快战斗，强力连击</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造无可匹敌的强力“大哥”，叠属性、上BUFF，比BOSS更像BOSS！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/03965d2d083f55f4e507474f841f5bff.poster.avif?t=1770945548\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/03965d2d083f55f4e507474f841f5bff.webm?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/03965d2d083f55f4e507474f841f5bff.mp4?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >技能联动，超爽combo，无限回合、大数字……皆有可能！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强力搭配，爽快割草，横扫千军，一招清屏不是梦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/fa87920c929884ca291b524020ea8f17.poster.avif?t=1770945548\" width=800 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/fa87920c929884ca291b524020ea8f17.webm?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/fa87920c929884ca291b524020ea8f17.mp4?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>花样构筑，就是上头</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由搭配卡牌与宝物，构建你的最强牌组。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200+卡牌，打造专属于你的致胜卡组！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+宝物，搭配出花样联动效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关副本，解锁9位能力各异的英雄。</p></li></ul></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量随机事件，让每一局冒险都充满变数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/c4ba9ad26567a8ac1333124cf85eb0f8.poster.avif?t=1770945548\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/c4ba9ad26567a8ac1333124cf85eb0f8.webm?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/c4ba9ad26567a8ac1333124cf85eb0f8.mp4?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富模式，挑战升级</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样冒险：固定Boss章节、随机Boss章节、每日挑战，总有一款你爱玩！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阶梯式难度：10+难度等级，见证你在冒险中的不断成长。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >表演模式：表演时间到！在高压关卡中验证你的最强构筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/6d249be7e0d0465f60634c2fd93697bc.poster.avif?t=1770945548\" width=850 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/6d249be7e0d0465f60634c2fd93697bc.webm?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/6d249be7e0d0465f60634c2fd93697bc.mp4?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>秀大哥，晒爽局，一键分享</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩偶码系统：分享你精心养成的“大哥”，谁看了都得膜拜！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战局分享：生成战斗码，分享精彩瞬间，让朋友见识什么叫“我的回合还没完”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/0b03d8fadbcbd767f5f7e632456d1240.poster.avif?t=1770945548\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/0b03d8fadbcbd767f5f7e632456d1240.webm?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332600/extras/0b03d8fadbcbd767f5f7e632456d1240.mp4?t=1770945548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
